{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "bootstrap",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## bootstrap.Run()\n`internal/bootstrap/bootstrap.go`\n\n- Builds registry, key store, config\n- Creates `*Gateway`\n- Calls `httpserver.NewRouter(..., gw, ...)`",
      "x": -920,
      "y": -680,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "new-router",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## NewRouter(...)\n`internal/httpserver/router.go:31`\n\n- `ensureGateway(gw, registry)`\n- `chi.NewRouter()`\n- Middleware stack\n- **mountOpenAIRoutes(r, gw, ...)**",
      "x": -920,
      "y": -460,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "middleware",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Global chi stack\n`router.go:52–68`\n\n- OTel, logging, recover\n- CORS, rate-limit",
      "x": -920,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "mount-openai",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## mountOpenAIRoutes()\n`router.go:194`\n\n- ProxyAuth middleware\n- **POST /v1/chat/completions**\n- GET /v1/models, other /v1/*",
      "x": -920,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "post-route",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## POST /v1/chat/completions\n`router.go:200`\n\n`r.Post(..., handler.ChatCompletions(gw))`\n\n- Auth required\n- Closes over `*Gateway`",
      "x": -920,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "gateway",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## *aigateway.Gateway\n`gateway.go:51`\n\n- RWMutex + provider map\n- Strategy + plugins\n- `Route(ctx, req)`\n- `RouteStream(ctx, req)`\n- FindByModel / FindStreamingByModel",
      "x": -920,
      "y": 480,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 220,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "chat-completions",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## ChatCompletions(gw)\n`internal/handler/chat.go:14`\n\n1. `DecodeChatCompletionRequest(r.Body)`\n2. `req.Validate()`\n3. Branch on `req.Stream`",
      "x": -500,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "decode",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## DecodeChatCompletionRequest\n`internal/handler/chatrequest.go:87`\n\n- Pool get wire DTO\n- JSON decode\n- Map messages\n- Return `providers.Request`",
      "x": -100,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "wire-dto",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## routeChatCompletionRequest\n`chatrequest.go:13`\n\nWire DTO — 19 fields\nBoth token fields copied out",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 340,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "validate",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## req.Validate()\n`providers/core/chat.go:192`\n\n- model, messages required\n- `max_tokens > 0`\n- **`max_completion_tokens > 0`**",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 80,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 180,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "error-node",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## apierror.WriteOpenAI\n\n400 decode / validation\n400 model not found\nRoute errors",
      "x": 320,
      "y": -180,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "request-obj",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## providers.Request\n`providers/core/chat.go:149`\n\n**Output limits (#141):**\n- `MaxTokens` → `\"max_tokens\"`\n- `MaxCompletionTokens` → `\"max_completion_tokens\"`\n\nAlso: Model, Messages, Stream, Tools…\n\n✅ Both survive decode + validation\n❌ Drop happens in provider layer",
      "x": -460,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "fork-label",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**if req.Stream**",
      "x": -260,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "streaming",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## req.Stream == true\n`chat.go:27–44`\n\n- FindByModel\n- FindStreamingByModel\n- **RouteStream(ctx, req)**\n- sse.Write\n\nTODO: provider mapping",
      "x": -860,
      "y": 860,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "non-streaming",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## req.Stream == false\n`chat.go:47–64`\n\n- FindByModel\n- **Route(ctx, req)**\n- JSON encode response\n\nTODO: provider mapping",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 860,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 200,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "note",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "**Issue #141 checkpoint (ingress):**\nBoth token fields ride into Route / RouteStream unchanged. Drop is per-provider.",
      "x": -460,
      "y": 860,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "3"
    }
  ],
